gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Tell a story many times, but it's inside that's really hurt;
In the body, there's fear, not in the limb or tongue.

Here is the translation:

Good to understand blessed saint's pleasure, accepted Lord's explicit promise;
My master's natural joy is like happiness, that very thing is our best good.

I have died in my death, you have not decided in your mind; 
Who will go back to meet halfway; 
He says within ourselves that saint, worships this moment, the God.

Here is the translation:

The village's treasure was plundered, nothing of value was left behind; 
In this way, we have been separated from happiness, go, O monks, slowly slowly.
